_sText:
The big 16 floor apartment house with custom textures, in real life it located near my house.

:::::::::: install instructions :::::::::::

1. .vmf file
Put into C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\"your account name"\sourcesdk\bin\ep1\bin\prefabs

2. textures
Put into C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\"your account name"\counter-strike source\cstrike\materials

::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

If you use this prefab, please credit me
